Speaker 2: Got it.

Speaker 1: No, yeah.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: Got it.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 2: Got it.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: And I don't...

Speaker 1: And I want to talk to your supervisor, whoever it is, I need to talk to the supervisor.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: Have them reach out to me.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: That would be great.

Speaker 2: They'll reach out to you when they're back in the office.

Speaker 1: Other than that, just wait for a call either later today or tomorrow.

Speaker 2: I'm not too sure when they'll be back exactly, but they should be back soon.

Speaker 1: Okay.
